metadata.name: Dare to Dream
metadata.description:
For all you dreamers out there, dare to dream and dream big. 

Close your eyes and let your imagination run wild, picture yourself where you want to be one day. Don't let someone else put a limit on your thoughts, because anything you want to achieve is possible if you want it enough. 

Delve into the mysteries of the universe. Let your heart guide you to where you want to be. Life is short, never stop searching, working hard for what you believe in and achieving your goals. 

Your dreams are yours and yours alone.
